# ----------------------------------------------------------------------------
# FILE: 	lms_trx_pcie_timing.sdc
# DESCRIPTION:	Timing constrains file for TimeQuest
# DATE:	June 2, 2017
# AUTHOR(s):	Lime Microsystems
# REVISIONS:
